### Get demo token
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/demo-token

### Create order
POST http://localhost:8000/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "customer_id": "CUST-101",
  "product_id": "P1001",
  "quantity": 2,
  "amount": 149.99
}

### Check inventory
GET http://localhost:8002/inventory/P1001

### Check notifications
GET http://localhost:8004/notifications
